		<tr>
			<td colspan="6" class="DetailTitle" style="text-align:center;">
                            Summary on Grant Application Form</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td colspan="6" class="DetailValue" style="padding:5px;">
                        <span id="lblAbstract">We are presenting an exciting new calculator at the Royal Society Summer Exhibition. It is a hands-on interactive exhibit that shows how calculators could work in the future, and also demonstrates cutting-edge computer science .Our research may well change the way basic arithmetic is taught in schools; it will certainly challenge calculator manufacturers to reform their approaches to handheld calculator design. Our prototypes of the calculator, despite being a  boring  simple application, have brought smiles and excitement to users, so we believe we have found some interesting research questions: why is it exciting; can we build on this excitement to make a durable product or interaction style that would stand up to daily use in, say, a school environment?</span>
                        </td>
		</tr>
